"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"## 介绍\\n\\n去中心化交易所，DEX，支持ar和马蹄，本次教程马蹄链上操作。\\n\\n官方推特：\\n\\n[https://twitter.com/SlingshotCrypto](https://twitter.com/SlingshotCrypto)\\n\\n## 交互步骤\\n\\n1、打开网站，右上角链接钱包，Metamask选择马蹄链。没有马蹄链的朋友，去chainlist添加，然后交易所去转账，不会的朋友，教程底部联系我。\\n\\n[https://app.slingshot.finance/trade/m/MATIC](https://app.slingshot.finance/trade/m/MATIC)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/Bb0o1O9rTV5Fg5ZFsede5.png?height=853&width=1909)\\n\\n2、页面左上角，输入买入金额，然后点击ReviewOrder按钮，如下图\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/Y5ytGRE68NmoMbxZxuDKU.png?height=851&width=1905)\\n\\n提示你解锁本次交易，点击确认\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/etvBg5lYODRLbNuH2MrPj.png?height=841&width=1896)\\n\\n等待完成\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/WAiCFUUDWgfXx11XnnPiJ.png?height=822&width=1764)\\n\\n再次弹出弹窗确认交易金额信息，确认无误后点击Place Order\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/dn7h5lhbAfKP6gu2Rch98.png?height=848&width=1881)\\n\\n等待\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/8f6g6trqt0KcdHaA7brx3.png?height=828&width=1839)\\n\\n出现下图则表示交易成功\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/yMXCxc8RJoJIHl0OvbUBu.png?height=844&width=1889)\\n\\n3、重复上面步骤，买入+卖出，最好总金额大于1000u，狠狠的刷上几笔\\n\\n4、这个项目还有聊天功能，有兴趣的可以聊上几句\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/_N5iV45LXg4rUeBV-vsfP.png?height=843&width=1899)\\n\\n**联系我：**\\n\\nweibo:\\n\\n[https://weibo.com/u/6448925810](https://weibo.com/u/6448925810)\\n\\ntwitter：\\n\\n[https://twitter.com/zhangzhun132](https://twitter.com/zhangzhun132)\\n\\n\",\"timestamp\":1639837314,\"title\":\"Slingshot交互教程--马蹄链\"},\"digest\":\"QfZTShJ26dWinmOfuSButWvBgyx3AIqBt-idkOVJpHc\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xeFD52a9E454FEB9Ad8edCA588c7a9703d67cdFF7\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"5J_WHlGX5HxNBSL-GNn7IE0J6Pn_QpBrolgmffoahUY\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"b5UyI3OXynUJBUZ1pz4jPgA6_eiQCpm7VitE1VFvr-s\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"RUUCUbZO3n_0-czvOrBrt7vNbbUk3dgkcgG0DSXyj1Px1pTpLY7US6WToVC-KkTEX2pI7v3gVAXk2aYjcWj1FQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x55954191cbb250f904bec526d0ae7668474194d100823cb2d2655442a1eaf7e577ada1e1dd8d1902bff040bf0e9e318b5c5f02313d8ac1648265f7c4afd1ea5c1b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"5J_WHlGX5HxNBSL-GNn7IE0J6Pn_QpBrolgmffoahUY\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"b5UyI3OXynUJBUZ1pz4jPgA6_eiQCpm7VitE1VFvr-s\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"JJSbklEJ-BVSgsGQm_lY6wJBI73Rnoo_4izzVFI-0Ms\"}"